    description:
      "Spearheaded a React Native mobile app for sales and inventory management, supporting 1,000+ businesses. Built a Next.js admin dashboard for FMCG brand analytics with GraphQL APIs. Engineered an MCP server for natural language database queries.",
    tags: ["React Native", "Next.js", "Node.js", "MongoDB", "GraphQL", "AWS"],
    current: true,
  },
  {
    title: "Fullstack Web Engineer",
    company: "Thelix Holdings (CreditVeto)",
    companyUrl: "https://thelixholdings.com",
    period: "Oct 2024 — Dec 2024",
    description:
      "Collaborated on a credit repair tool for U.S. citizens. Shipped AI Credit Summary by integrating Array and OpenAI ChatGPT with caching to cut cost and response time. Accelerated delivery by leveraging AI tools.",
    tags: ["Next.js", "NestJS", "PostgreSQL", "OpenAI"],
    current: false,
  },
  {
    title: "Fullstack Engineer / React Native Engineer",
    company: "Learnpally",
    companyUrl: "https://www.learnpally.com",
    period: "Feb 2024 — Aug 2025",
    description:
      "Led a team of engineers building a Coursera-like e-learning platform with React Native mobile and React web apps. Architected adaptive video streaming (420p–1080p) and integrated Stripe and Flutterwave for payments.",
    tags: ["React", "React Native", "Node.js", "MongoDB", "Stripe"],
    current: false,
  },
  {
    title: "Fullstack Engineer / UX Engineer",
    company: "Future Academy Africa",
    companyUrl: "https://www.futureacademy.africa",
    period: "May 2022 — Feb 2024",
    description:
      "Developed an e-learning platform handling 5,000+ student registrations. Enhanced landing page UX, increasing session duration by 30%. Taught front-end development to 500+ learners.",
    tags: ["React", "Next.js", "Nuxt.js", "Node.js", "MongoDB"],
    current: false,
  },
  {
    title: "Fullstack Engineer",
    company: "EduLight Consulting",
    companyUrl: "https://www.edulightconsulting.com.ng",
    period: "Aug 2017 — Jan 2022",
    description:
      "Led development of Snappy Exchange, a crypto exchange platform handling billions in transactions. Built and deployed 5+ web applications across finance, e-commerce, and HR domains. Migrated legacy PHP systems to Vue and Node.js.",
